⠀⠀⢸⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣷⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠘⠉⠉⠙⣿⣿⣿⣷⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢸⣿⣿⣿⣧⠀⠀     aziz programming language.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣼⣿⣿⣿⣿⣆⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣼⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⡀     a subset of common lisp
⠀⠀⠀⠀⣴⣿⣿⣿⠟⣿⣿⣿⣷     implemented with xDSL.
⠀⠀⠀⣰⣿⣿⣿⡏⠀⠸⣿⣿⣿⣇ 
⠀⠀⢠⣿⣿⣿⡟⠀⠀⠀⢻⣿⣿⣿⡆
⠀⢠⣿⣿⣿⡿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢿⣿⣿⣷⣤⡄
⢀⣾⣿⣿⣿⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⠿⣿⣿⣿⡇

usage:

```
find examples -name "*.aziz"


uv run aziz-lang/main.py examples/hello.aziz --target=aziz-lowered --mlir # broken
uv run aziz-lang/main.py examples/if.aziz --target=aziz-lowered --mlir
uv run aziz-lang/main.py examples/optimize.aziz --target=aziz-lowered --mlir
uv run aziz-lang/main.py examples/rec.aziz --target=aziz-lowered --mlir # broken
uv run aziz-lang/main.py examples/test.aziz --target=aziz-lowered --mlir
```

